  "abstract": "(57) [Abstract] [Purpose] High-temperature performance by improving the non-aqueous electrolyte,  It is an object to provide a lithium secondary battery having excellent storage performance, rate characteristics and cycle life. A lithium secondary battery comprising a positive electrode, a negative electrode containing a lithium metal, a carbonaceous material that occludes and releases lithium ions, a chalcogen compound or a light metal, and a non-aqueous electrolyte, wherein the non-aqueous electrolyte is 10-80% by volume of at least one solvent selected from ethylene carbonate and propylene carbonate and 20-90% by volume of at least one solvent selected from diethoxyethane, chain carbonate and acetonitrile.  In a non-aqueous solvent prepared by mixing with, the formula Li (C n X 2n + 1 Y) 2 N  (Where X is a halogen, n is an integer of 1 to 4, and Y is a CO group or SO 2 group) and has a composition in which 0.1 to 3 mol / l of an imide lithium salt is dissolved. I am trying.",
